
'''''Nairobi Half Life''''' ni film y'ikinamico yo muri Kenya yasohotse 2012 iyobowe na David "Tosh" Gitonga<ref>https://www.trigon-film.org/en/movies/Nairobi_Half_Life</ref>. Iyi filime yatoranijwe nka filime yo muri kenya yinjiye neza mu rurimi rw'amahanga muri Oscar  mu bihembo bya 85 bya Osama<ref>https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/general-news/nairobi-life-afi-fest-review-391847/</ref>, ariko ntiyaboneka  k'urutonde rwa nyuma, kandi ni ubwa mbere Kenya itanga filime muri iki cyiciro<ref>https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/nairobi_half_life_2012</ref>. Mu iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya Filime rya 33 rya Durban, Joseph Wairimu yatsindiye igihembo cy'umukinnyi mwiza<ref>https://www.showmax.com/eng/movie/48wfzimm-nairobi-half-life</ref>.  Yatsindiye kandi igihembo cya Afurika Movie Academy igihembo cy'umukinnyi wizewe cyane kuva mu birori bya 9<ref>https://africanfilmny.org/films/nairobi-half-life/</ref> . Yatsindiye ibihembo byinshi muri Afrika Magic Viewers Choice Awards 2014 <ref>https://www.standardmedia.co.ke/entertainment/nainotepad/2001264050/being-famous-doesnt-pay-rent-nairobi-half-life-actor-joseph-mwas-wairimu</ref>. 

