== Kwakira ==
''Umunyamakuru wa Hollywood,'' Todd McCarthy, yashimye iyi filime nyuma yo kuyireba muri AFI Fest 2012<ref>https://www.cnn.com/2012/11/09/world/africa/kenya-film-nairobi-half-life/index.html</ref>: "Iyi kinamico  igaragaramo  ubunyangamugayo bufatika ."  KenyaBuzz yerekanye imikorere yibye yakozwe na Maina Olwenya ubwo Oti yagize ati: "Iyi mico ni ghetto kuruta kumva alubumu za kera za NWA. Avuga ko afite ubugizi bwa nabi kandi agenda nkaho atunze umujyi nubwo ari umugizi wa nabi<ref>http://www.africine.org/film/nairobi-half-life/14212</ref>. "Muri Werurwe 2014 Afurika Magic Viewers Choice Awards muri Werurwe 2014,  ''Nairobi Half Life'' yahawe ibihembo kuri<ref>https://www.dw.com/en/my-first-film-shows-nairobi-how-it-really-is/a-16301832</ref>: 

* Umukinnyi wa Sinema mwiza (Christian Almesberger)
* Igishushanyo Cyiza cyo Kumurika (Mohamed Zain)
* Umuhanzi mwiza wo kwisiga (Elayne Okaya) na
* Umuyobozi mwiza wubuhanzi ( Barbara Minishi ).

